data.description: Stunning 4-bed, 2-bath home in the desirable River Bend subdivision. Spanning 2078 sq ft, this residence offers versatility with the 4th bedroom doubling as an office or bedroom. Enjoy peace of mind with a two-year-old roof and a 2018 HVAC system backed by a 10-year parts warranty. The property boasts new carpet, paint, and engineered wood plank flooring, creating a fresh and modern ambiance. The kitchen comes complete with a refrigerator, and the laundry area includes a dryer – both staying with the home. Experience the outdoors in a spacious fenced backyard with a covered patio, perfect for entertaining. The living room features vaulted ceilings adorned with natural wood beams, adding a touch of character. Additionally, the formal dining room and breakfast area provide ample space for family gatherings. The large master bedroom is a retreat with French doors leading to the backyard and covered patio. This residence combines comfort, style, and functionality!
